column20: Dashami Anushtana Harivasara starts at 11.43 PM

Sri Parasurama Jayanthi, Akshaya Truthiya, Tretha Yugadi, Sri Vidyadhirajar Aradhane (Yaragola), Sri Vidyapathi Theerthar Aradhane (Kumbakonam), Sri Vidya Srinivasa Theerthar Aradhane (Sosale), Sri Vijayadhwaja Theerthar Aradhane (Kanvatheertha)
Vaisakha Snana Poorthi, Sri Rajendra Theerthar Aradhane (Yaragola)
Prathama Ekadasi (Sayana Ekadasi), Taptha Mudra Dharana , Shaka Vratha Arambha
Dwadasi - Till 8:36 a.m Harivasara Pancha Kavya Praasanam, Sri Sripathi Theerthar Aradhane (Rayavellore)
Kataka Sankramana, Dhakshinayana Punya kaala, Snana tharpana afternoon
Ekadasi Upavasa, Sri Vidyanidhi Theerthar Aradhane (Sosale)
Gokulashtami Upavasa, Pooje, Arghya at night
Vijayadasami, Buddha Jayanthi, Sri Madhwa Jayanthi
Yama Dwithiya, Bhojanam at Sister's house, Sri Vidyasamudra Theerthara Aradhane (Sosale)
Pakini Truthiya - Bhojanam at brother's house
Chaturmasa Vratha ends, Sri Vidyavachaspathi Theerthar Aradhane (Thirumookadalu)
Ekadasi Upavasa - Bheeshmapagna Vratha Aaramba, Sri Lakshmipathi Theerthara Aradhane (Srirangam)
Uthana Dwadasi - Sri Tulasi Sri Krishan Vivaha, Swayambu Manvathi
Sri Lakshmi Narayana Theerthara Aradhane (Badarikasrama Pravesha)
Kaarthika Snaana Samapthi - Sri Vyasa Pooje, Sri Jayathvaja Theerthar Aradhane (Yaragola)
Sri Mahipathi Dasara Aradhane (Kakandaki), Amavasya Thilatharpana
Sri Sankarshana Wodeyaru Aradhane (Karampoondi) - Wrote Prose to Sri Harikathamruthasara
Amavasya Thila Tharpana, Sri Hanumantha Jayanthi in Tamilnadu
Vaikunta Ekadasi, Sri Ragothama Theerthara Aradhane (Manampoondi/Thirukovilur)
Dwadasi Parane - Dhanur Maasa Pooje Ends
Uttarayana Punya Kaala - Tharpana till 11:12 a.m
Amavasya Thila tharpana, Sri Purandara Dasara Aradhane (Hampi)
Amavasya - Thila Tharpanam, Day when Sri Vyasarajar did Kuha Yoga Parihara for Krishnadevaraya
Sri Vadiraja Swamigala Aradhane (Sode), Sri Vyasaraja Swamigala Poorvaradhane
Sri Vyasaraja Swamigala Uttara Aradhane, Sri Govinda Wodeyaru Aradhane (Navabrindavana)
Meena Sankramana Punyakaala Tharpana from morning
